document_data.mainbody:
anner Alley was a small alley that was located in the city of Waterdeep during the 15 century DR.
Tanner Alley was located in the eastern section of Waterdeeps Field Ward. It ran between Gawenknife Street in the west with Stench Alley and Logans Walk in the east. Tanner Alley branched several times.
